      "text": "deploy-staging.yml\n\nChange detection\n(infra / frontend / services)\n\nDocker build ARM64\ntag: {sha:7}-staging.{run}\n\nECR push\n\u2192 188701360969.dkr.ecr\n   eu-central-1.amazonaws.com\n\nCDK diff + deploy\n\nECS rolling deploy\n\u2192 health check \u2705",
